Doors will be identified by a door number consisting of 2 parts i.e.
Room number and D1, D2, D3 and etc. E.g. If the room number is
A1006 the door will be labelled A1006.D1 if only one door is
applicable to the room. If there is more than one door per room the
door number will be A1006.D1, A1006.D2 etc.
